  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Multi-Tool</span>. This weapon comes equipped with the versatile <span class=\"name name-technology\">Neutron Cannon</span>, which delivers powerful volleys of atmospheric particles - the longer it is charged, the more deadly the blast.<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">Take</span> this Multi-Tool to add it to your collection, or <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exchange</span> it with your current Multi-Tool. Swap between active Multi-Tools from the Utilities section of the Quick Menu (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>).",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">多用途工具</span>。这款武器配备了多功能<span class=\"name name-technology\">中子大炮</span>，可以发射强大的大气粒子，充能时间越长，爆炸杀伤力越大。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">收下</span>这个多用途工具，将它加入你的收藏，或与你现在的多用途工具<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交换</span>。在快捷菜单（<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>）中的工具部分切换可用的多用途工具。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一個特殊<span class=\"name name-stellar\">工具組</span>。這把武器搭載了多用途<span class=\"name name-technology\">中子砲</span>，能夠發射一道強大的大氣粒子，充能時間越長，射擊就越致命。<br><br><span class=\"name name-stellar\">取走</span>這個工具組加入你的收藏，或是與目前工具組<span class=\"name name-stellar\">交換</span>。在星球上時，利用快捷選單 (<span class=\"name name-img\">QUICK_MENU</span>) 中的機能頁面切換使用中的工具組。"
  },
